headline: FIS Celebrated With Two Major Honors at 2025 Global Finance Treasury & Cash Management Awards
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., August 28, 2025--FIS® (NYSE:FIS), a global leader in financial technology, was recognized with two major accolades at the 2025 Global Finance Treasury and Cash Management Systems and Services Awards. FIS Treasury and Risk Manager - Integrity Edition received the title of "Most Innovative Treasury Solution," while FIS Treasury and Risk Manager - Quantum Cloud Edition was named "Best Treasury Management Software."
